node.text: Dang Joe...words cannot ever express my sincere love, respect, sisterhood, loyalty or musical aspirations for you! You’re loved by so many people, but that’s just one of your gifts. Love you my Shucky! #DuckyQuackQuack #Chucklife #NinthStreetTunnel #DCLegend #Hitmen thank you frenn @niccigilbert for this! ❤️

node.text: Dang Joe...words cannot ever express my sincere love, respect, sisterhood, loyalty or musical aspirations for you! You’re loved by so many people, but that’s just one of your gifts. Love you my Shucky! #DuckyQuackQuack #Chucklife #NinthStreetTunnel #DCLegend #Hitmen thank you frenn @niccigilbert for this! ❤️
